data.description: Calera Schools!  This home has a fenced backyard, providing an ideal space for both privacy and outdoor enjoyment. Arriving home is a breeze with the convenience of a 2-car garage offering main-level parking.Step inside and discover a versatile flex space, perfect for an office or formal dining area. The kitchen features stainless appliances, granite countertops, a walk-in pantry, and a generously sized island/breakfast bar. The open concept floor plan seamlessly integrates a separate dining space, creating a harmonious flow into the family room.Take the staircase to the upper level, where you will find A spacious laundry room that is thoughtfully placed near the bedrooms for ease and efficiency. The primary bedroom is a retreat in itself, offering an oversized haven. The primary bath exudes opulence with its separate garden tub, large walk-in shower, and double vanities. Three well-appointed guest bedrooms provide ample space for family or visitors, complemented by a full bath.
